♪At the end of the universe, we embark on another journey yet again♪

26
00:02:11,020 --> 00:02:15,940
[The Blood of Youth: Quest of Heroic Hearts]

27
00:02:15,980 --> 00:02:18,980
[Episode 14]

28
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:20,680
Lei Lingze.

29
00:02:21,480 --> 00:02:22,720
It's best if you stay here.

30
00:02:28,520 --> 00:02:29,720
Do you all think

31
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:31,800
I'm a fool?

32
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:46,920
I'm not a fool.

33
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:53,080
I believe in the way

34
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,200
of heroism.

35
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,000
And heroism

36
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,360
is about helping the weak.

37
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,960
The heroism you speak of

38
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,800
is nothing more than hot-headed recklessness.

39
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:12,240
To be a hero,

40
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,840
one must learn to protect oneself.

41
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,600
So, standing here idly as someone dies

42
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:16,920
is what you think a hero should do?

43
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:21,680
Unlike you, I'm not someone cold-blooded

44
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:24,080
who has lost his past memory.

45
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,160
If I don't intervene now,

46
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,120
this world

47
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,000
might see the loss

48
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,440
of another innocent life.

49
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:39,000
Lei Lingze!

50
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:39,480
Weigui.

51
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,200
Calm down.

52
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:51,080
Help!

53
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:54,320
Can someone save me?

54
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:00,600
Help me!

55
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,600
It's fake?

56
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,440
Something's wrong

57
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:50,360
with the noise.

58
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:54,000
It can turn someone violent.

59
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:57,280
Perhaps Lei Lingze was influenced by it

60
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:59,000
and then argued with me.

61
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,840
Someone in my sect set up

62
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:02,280
the Peach Blossom Enchantment Array behind my back

63
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,560
to disorient the enemies.

64
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:08,600
Lei Lingze.

65
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,120
Why am I all tied up?

66
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:37,880
Who are you?

67
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:39,280
Release me now.

68
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,520
[Green-robed Woman]
Relax.

69
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,200
Now is not the time yet.

70
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,560
Why did you

71
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:52,800
lure me here?

72
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:55,120
For the Skysplitter, of course.

73
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,680
Take a good look at me.

74
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,400
Do I have the Skysplitter?

75
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:02,240
I know your friend has it,

76
00:06:02,640 --> 00:06:05,200
so I'm using you as the bait.

77
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:06,920
You...

78
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:09,800
Miss,

79
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,360
I'll have to disappoint you.

80
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,280
Weigui.

81
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,320
Surrender the Skysplitter

82
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:25,960
or none of you can leave.

83
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:33,840
Reinforcement from the Peach Blossom Array?

84
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,720
You'll have to get the Skysplitter

85
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:38,320
over my dead body.

86
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:42,480
Let me reiterate.

87
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,440
I only want the Skysplitter

88
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:47,320
because I want the senseless killing in the world to cease.

89
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,560
Father, come and find me.

90
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:51,640
Ever since

91
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:54,560
news of the Skysplitter fragments appeared,

92
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,080
Peach Blossom Haven has not seen a peaceful day.

93
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:59,280
Are you done hiding, my daughter?

94
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,840
I'm going to look for you.

95
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,160
Surrender the Skysplitter

96
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,320
and I'll spare you.

97
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,840
Who are you? What are you doing here?

98
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,520
I don't have any swords. Don't!

99
00:07:10,080 --> 00:07:10,840
I swear

100
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,720
to find the Skysplitter

101
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:15,120
to stop the tragedy from happening again.

102
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:18,440
Her reason

103
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:19,640
doesn't sound that bad.

104
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,600
Don't be deceived.

105
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,040
We've not seen

106
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,480
a villager after we arrived at Peach Blossom Village.

107
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:26,000
Unless...

108
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,760
Unless everyone here has died.

109
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:35,000
Yes.

110
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,960
They all died.

111
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:40,880
Died in the conflicts of the martial arts world.

112
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,680
Caught

113
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:45,120
between the greed of the so-called heroes.

114
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:47,200
So I'm putting an end to this.

115
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:48,720
If they are all dead,

116
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,720
why are you the only survivor?

117
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:53,000
Isn't that a bit odd?

118
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,880
If I'm not mistaken,

119
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:59,280
you're one of Tianwaitian.

120
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:01,360
You're lying to me

121
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,400
to get the Skysplitter.

122
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:17,040
I remember

123
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:20,520
when you arrived at the peach blossom forest,

124
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:23,440
there was another girl with you.

125
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,120
Find Xiaohua now.

126
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:28,360
Make sure she is safe.

127
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:29,360
We'll take it from here.

128
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:44,640
At first, I just wanted you to give me the Skysplitter.

129
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:46,400
Now,

130
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,480
I want all of you dead.

131
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:17,600
Is someone there?

132
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:19,840
Help!

133
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,600
Is someone there?

134
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,240
Help!

135
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,720
Is someone there?

136
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:31,400
Is someone there?

137
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,480
Ye Zhixin.

138
00:09:35,760 --> 00:09:36,680
Save me.

139
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:40,080
Back off.

140
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,200
Are you all fine?

141
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:46,760
Why are you alone?

142
00:09:46,880 --> 00:09:47,320
Where are they?

143
00:09:47,680 --> 00:09:48,800
They are in the peach blossom forest still.

144
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,120
I know who did this.

145
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:52,240
Come. Let's inform them.

146
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,080
They are from Tianwaitian.

147
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,640
There is a peach blossom mark on their hands.

148
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:00,680
Ye Zhixin?

149
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:04,480
Ye Zhixin?

150
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:07,520
Ye Zhixin?

151
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,120
Whatever. I'll regroup with them first.

152
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:20,440
Weigui.

153
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,360
The lack of a sword can triumph over a sword,

154
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:32,000
for a sword is not the be-all and end-all.

155
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:32,920
