Weigui!

162
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:25,080
Weigui.

163
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:25,880
Are you all right?

164
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:27,400
Lei Lingze!

165
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:28,160
Weigui!

166
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:30,040
Lei Lingze.

167
00:12:31,560 --> 00:12:32,000
Weigui.

168
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:33,320
What happened to Weigui?

169
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:33,760
Weigui.

170
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:34,520
Weigui.

171
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:35,440
Weigui.

172
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:37,320
You're scaring me, Weigui.

173
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:39,000
Wake up.

174
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:39,480
Weigui.

175
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:40,560
You're scaring me.

176
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:41,800
Weigui.

177
00:12:46,680 --> 00:12:47,360
